snippet.title: Bachelairs - out now!
snippet.description:
In Bachelairs, race through a set of short dungeons and try to collect the most treasures. The player that has the most coins at the end wins the game! Will you horde your coins? Invest in stronger gear? Or perhaps try to win extra gold with one of the awards? Face off against friends or play against the computer!

Get it through

https://www.patreon.com/sokpop
https://sokpop.itch.io/bachelairs
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2948380/Bachelairs/
